{"tid":934940,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"示愛之禍 (張智霖『祝君好』改編) [新詞歌曲]","createTime":"2018-12-09T15:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T01:35:04.000Z","uid":190992,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06f558c717f8e4eeda676beaf3d50a2d00bb29bf","tid":934940,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"　澳門永遠是我們最喜愛的地方　祝你永遠幸福<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0vYWffuAUc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db0vYWffuAUc&d=9weJ2qoQPFEbcYmxTI9AOsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0129d36f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0vYWffuAUc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/bdhFgGP/profess-love2-snapshot-3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FbdhFgGP%2Fprofess-love2-snapshot-3.png&h=d60d5793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　示愛之禍 (張智霖『祝君好』改編) [新詞歌曲]<br />\n　填詞/主唱: 夢詞人  原唱:張智霖<br />\n<br />\n　對　你一定討厭我<br />\n　示愛　埋下了滔天大禍<br />\n　做朋友　簡單不過但我心<br />\n　多徒然　苦戀擱淺<br />\n<br />\n　錯　再三望你都錯<br />\n　夢碎全踏破不勝負荷<br />\n　回頭看　身份不過如路過<br />\n　走近了是我的錯<br />\n<br />\n＊從此沒相見　未妄想再見<br />\n　為何會和你大堂遇見　心底仍掛念<br />\n　期待某天新婚照片　依舊能望見你風姿翩翩<br />\n　雖風箏一早斷線<br />\n<br />\n　遠　縱使共你多遠<br />\n　念掛　長夜到清早未斷<br />\n　但求你　找到真愛能像我<br />\n　不歇送贈你溫暖<br />\n<br />\n　重複　＊<br />\n<br />\n　從此沒相見　就算情深不變<br />\n　為何會難卻盛情赴宴　悲歡難判辨<br />\n　凝望那張婚紗照片　依舊能望見你風姿翩翩<br />\n　當風箏不想斷線<br />\n<br />\n　#示愛之禍,#澳門,#十月初五,#主教山,#美食,#酒店,#祝君好,#張智霖,#新詞,#改編,#粵語歌,#MC2,#KT2,#情歌,#我的推介,#2018,#YouTube影片,#夢詞人頻道,#廣東歌,#cantopop,#music,#song,#songs,#melody,#newsong"},{"pid":"2e11e8dc80e705b4a06b9615cfa649d1990fe6bb","tid":934940,"uid":190992,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tX-YF-X44n0&amp;t=5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtX-YF-X44n0%26t%3D5s&d=9weJ2qoQPFEbcYmxTI9AOsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=8dcdbadc\"